java.lang.Object
org.apache.openjpa.jdbc.meta.QueryResultMapping
All Implemented Interfaces:
SourceTracker, Commentable, MetaDataModes
public class QueryResultMapping extends Object implements MetaDataModes, SourceTracker, Commentable
Mapping of a query result set to scalar and/or persistence-capable object-level values.
